# =================================================================
# PROJECT: The Accountant / Hive Core
# PURPOSE: Prevent environment bloat and cloud-sync conflicts
# =================================================================

### 1. VIRTUAL ENVIRONMENTS
# We keep these local-only to avoid symbolic link errors on Google Drive
venv/
.venv/
env/

### 2. PYTHON JUNK
# Compiled files and metadata that don't belong in version control
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
.python-version
notes.py

### 3. DISTRIBUTION / PACKAGING
# If you use 'pip install -e .', these folders will appear
*.egg-info/
dist/
build/

### 4. OPERATING SYSTEM FILES
# Trash files generated by Linux/Windows/macOS
.DS_Store
thumbs.db
.directory
*.swp

### 5. LOCAL CONFIG & SECRETS
# Never commit your API keys or local DB paths
.env
config.json
*.log
.csv
financial_snapshot.json
db.sqlite3

notes.txt

### 6. Needless Data
finance/data/
finance/logs/
finance/migrations/
